<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= lang %>">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Windows</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: #0000AA;
            color: #AAAAAA;
            font-family: 'Perfect DOS VGA 437', 'Fixedsys', 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            padding: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .header-bar {
            background: #AAAAAA;
            color: #0000AA;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .error-header {
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .message {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .stop-code {
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .separator {
            color: white;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .technical-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .instructions {
            margin-top: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid #AAAAAA;
        }

        .memory-address {
            color: white;
            font-family: monospace;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .qr-section {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .qr-code {
            background: #AAAAAA;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .qr-code img {
            display: block;
        }

        .qr-message {
            max-width: 170px;
            color: #AAAAAA;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                padding: 15px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .error-header {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .stop-code {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .qr-section {
                position: static;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }
        }

        /* Scan line effect for authenticity */
        @keyframes scanline {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(-100%);
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(100vh);
            }
        }

        body::after {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom,
                transparent,
                rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05),
                transparent
            );
            animation: scanline 6s linear infinite;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* CRT flicker effect */
        @keyframes flicker {
            0% { opacity: 0.98; }
            50% { opacity: 1; }
            100% { opacity: 0.98; }
        }

        body {
            animation: flicker 0.15s infinite;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header-bar">
            Windows
        </div>

        <div class="error-header">
            A problem has been detected and Windows has been shut down to prevent damage<br>
            to your computer.
        </div>

        <div class="message">
            <%= description %>
        </div>

        <div class="separator">
            ********************************************************************************
        </div>

        <div class="stop-code">
            *** STOP: <%= stopCode %>
        </div>

        <div class="technical-info">
            <%= technicalDetail %>
        </div>

        <div class="instructions">
            If this is the first time you've seen this stop error screen,<br>
            restart your computer. If this screen appears again, follow<br>
            these steps:<br>
            <br>
            Check to be sure you have adequate disk space. If a driver is<br>
            identified in the stop message, disable the driver or check<br>
            with the manufacturer for driver updates. Try changing video<br>
            adapters.<br>
            <br>
            Check with your hardware vendor for any BIOS updates. Disable<br>
            BIOS memory options such as caching or shadowing. If you need to<br>
            use Safe Mode to remove or disable components, restart your<br>
            computer, press F8 to select Advanced Startup Options, and then<br>
            select Safe Mode.
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            Technical information:<br>
            <br>
            *** STOP: 0x0000007B (0xF78D2524, 0xC0000034, 0x00000000, 0x00000000)
        </div>

        <div class="memory-address">
            Beginning dump of physical memory<br>
            Physical memory dump complete.<br>
            Contact your system administrator or technical support group for further<br>
            assistance.
        </div>
    </div>

    <% if (qrCode) { %>
    <div class="qr-section">
        <div class="qr-code">
            <img src="<%= qrCode %>" alt="QR Code">
        </div>
        <div class="qr-message">
            <%= qrMessage %>
        </div>
    </div>
    <% } %>

    <script>
        // Prevent scrolling
        document.addEventListener('touchmove', function(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
        }, { passive: false });

        // Easter egg: Press ESC to go to modern version
        document.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
            if (e.key === 'Escape') {
                window.location.href = '/?style=win11';
            }
            // F8 for "safe mode" (actually win7 style)
            if (e.key === 'F8') {
                window.location.href = '/?style=win7';
            }
        });

        // Random screen "glitch" for authenticity
        setInterval(() => {
            if (Math.random() > 0.95) {
                document.body.style.transform = 'translateX(' + (Math.random() * 4 - 2) + 'px)';
                setTimeout(() => {
                    document.body.style.transform = 'translateX(0)';
                }, 50);
            }
        }, 1000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
